OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FSchools cut Ofsted         
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Freferences in tribute to   
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5Fhead                       
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Head teachers are removing references  
OL,6, to Ofsted from websites, job adverts   
OL,7, and letters in tribute to a head who   
OL,8, killed herself after an inspection.    
OL,10,FRuth Perry's family have blamed her    
OL,11,Fdeath on the "intolerable pressure" of 
OL,12,Fthe inspection, which downgraded her   
OL,13,Fprimary school, in Reading, to         
OL,14,F"inadequate".                          
OL,16,FIt has led to widespread calls for     
OL,17,Freform of England's schools' watchdog. 
OL,19,FBut the government says Ofsted is      
OL,20,F"crucial" to maintaining standards.    
